sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?film <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film> . ?film <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/producer> ?uri . } ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?film)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

sparql2nl.en: What is the URI of the producer who has produced the most number of films in the database?
sparql2nl.prompt:
Assume you have to rephrase the following SPARQL query as a natural-language question for non-technical humans. 
Use the English language. SPARQL query: 
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?film <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film> . ?film <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/producer> ?uri . } ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?film)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
